   "analysis": "REFLECTION ANALYSIS:\nThe text is a sexually explicit erotic narrative depicting incest. It engages value 1.1 (Dignity) by systematically reducing the female character to a collection of sexualized body parts and fluids, treating her as an instrument for gratification rather than a person with inherent worth. The narrative frames the mother's loss of agency and sexual degradation as the source of pleasure, normalizing objectification for entertainment purposes.",
